sentence: find a flight from washington d c to boston
sq2:
SELECT DISTINCT  '"'||v0.flight_id||'"', '"'||v1.airport_code||'"',
 '"'||v2.city_code||'"', '"'||v2.city_name||'"', '"'||v3.state_code||'"',
 '"'||v4.airport_code||'"', '"'||v5.city_code||'"',
 '"'||v5.city_name||'"' FROM flight v0, airport_service v1,
 city v2, state v3, airport_service v4, city v5 
WHERE (((v0.from_airport = ANY v1.airport_code) 
AND ((v1.city_code = ANY v2.city_code) 
AND ((v2.city_name = 'WASHINGTON') 
AND ((v2.state_code = ANY v3.state_code) AND (v3.state_code = 'DC'))))) 
AND ((v0.to_airport = ANY v4.airport_code) AND ((v4.city_code = ANY v5.city_code) 
AND (v5.city_name = 'BOSTON'))));
